vernac_cmds: Lemma ordered_dynamic_uninitialized_state : forall net failed tr, step_ordered_dynamic_failure_star step_ordered_dynamic_failure_init (failed, net) tr -> forall n, ~ In n (odnwNodes net) -> odnwState net n = None.
induction H using refl_trans_1n_trace_n1_ind => H_init /=; first by rewrite H_init.
match goal with | [ H : step_ordered_dynamic_failure _ _ _ |- _ ] => invc H end; rewrite /=.
have H_neq: h <> n by move => H_eq; case: H_in; left.
have H_not_in: ~ In n (odnwNodes net0) by move => H_not_in; case: H_in; right.
case name_eq_dec => H_dec; first by rewrite H_dec in H_neq.
have H_neq: n <> to by move => H_eq; rewrite H_eq in H_in.
have H_neq: n <> h by move => H_eq; rewrite H_eq in H_in.

Lemma ordered_dynamic_initialized_state : forall net failed tr, step_ordered_dynamic_failure_star step_ordered_dynamic_failure_init (failed, net) tr -> forall n, In n (odnwNodes net) -> exists d, odnwState net n = Some d.
induction H using refl_trans_1n_trace_n1_ind => H_init /=; first by rewrite H_init.
match goal with | [ H : step_ordered_dynamic_failure _ _ _ |- _ ] => invc H end; rewrite /=.
have H_neq: n <> h by move => H_eq; rewrite H_eq in H_in.

Lemma ordered_dynamic_failed_then_initialized : forall net failed tr, step_ordered_dynamic_failure_star step_ordered_dynamic_failure_init (failed, net) tr -> forall n, In n failed -> In n (odnwNodes net).
have H_eq_o: net = snd (failed, net) by [].
induction H using refl_trans_1n_trace_n1_ind => H_init /=; first by rewrite H_init.
match goal with | [ H : step_ordered_dynamic_failure _ _ _ |- _ ] => invc H end; rewrite /=.
case: H_in => H_in; first by rewrite -H_in.

Lemma ordered_dynamic_state_not_initialized_not_failed : forall net failed tr, step_ordered_dynamic_failure_star step_ordered_dynamic_failure_init (failed, net) tr -> forall n, ~ In n (odnwNodes net) -> ~ In n failed.
have H_eq_o: net = snd (failed, net) by [].
induction H using refl_trans_1n_trace_n1_ind => H_init /=; first by rewrite H_init.
match goal with | [ H : step_ordered_dynamic_failure _ _ _ |- _ ] => invc H end; rewrite /=.
have H_not_in: ~ In n (odnwNodes net0) by move => H_in'; case: H_in; right.
case: H_or => H_or; first by repeat find_rewrite.

Lemma ordered_dynamic_no_outgoing_uninitialized : forall onet failed tr, step_ordered_dynamic_failure_star step_ordered_dynamic_failure_init (failed, onet) tr -> forall n, ~ In n (odnwNodes onet) -> forall n', onet.(odnwPackets) n n' = [].
induction H using refl_trans_1n_trace_n1_ind => H_init /=; first by rewrite H_init.
match goal with | [ H : step_ordered_dynamic_failure _ _ _ |- _ ] => invc H end; rewrite /=.
have H_neq: h <> n by eauto.
have H_not_in: ~ In n (odnwNodes net0) by eauto.
rewrite collate_ls_not_in; first by rewrite collate_neq //; eauto.
have H_neq: to <> n by move => H_eq; rewrite -H_eq in H_a.
case sumbool_and => H_and; last by eauto.
have H_neq: h <> n by move => H_eq; rewrite -H_eq in H_a.
have H_neq: h <> n by move => H_eq; rewrite -H_eq in H_a.
Lemma ordered_dynamic_nodes_no_dup : forall onet failed tr, step_ordered_dynamic_failure_star step_ordered_dynamic_failure_init (failed, onet) tr -> NoDup (odnwNodes onet).
match goal with | [ H : step_ordered_dynamic_failure _ _ _ |- _ ] => invc H end; rewrite //=.
